        I'm Will. I'm an engineer first, CEO second. I co-founded
        <a href="https://exadev.io">ExaDev</a> in 2013 with Francis Williams while we were both doing our PhDs at Bangor.
        We started in a bedroom with nothing but laptops and stubbornness, and grew it into a 17-strong technical
