      </p>

      <p>
        ExaDev builds companies, not just software. We embed small, senior engineering teams directly into early-stage
        startups, acting as fractional CTOs, tech leads, and hands-on builders. No management overhead, no tech-adjacent
        roles. Engineers are the decision makers. Through our investment arm
        <a href="https://exacap.io">ExaCap</a>, we take equity stakes to align our incentives with our clients' long-term
        success. The startups we've worked with have collectively raised over &pound;77m.
      </p>

      <p>
        I completed my PhD in Unsupervised Change Detection part-time over seven years while building the business.
        That experience taught me the value of quiet diligence over loud promises. Along the way I've worked as
        a developer, infrastructure engineer, data scientist, data engineer, machine learning engineer, and tech lead.
        I still can't make my mind up which I like most.
      </p>

